ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Take this class much rather than Econometrics II because it is just as applied but also has the theoretical rigor. Superb Professor teaching it.
I'd strongly recommend this course to those who are willing to do applied econometrics. It clarifies what is the identification issues are, which is, I think, the core concept of econometrics.
I will because it's such a wonderful course.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It was essential to my research
I believe this course helps my future research.
It deepened my understanding in theoretical and applied econometrics, which is essential when conducting economic research.
